Package project2.starsApp

Class Admin

java.lang.Object
project2.starsApp.User
project2.starsApp.Admin
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, AdminCourseManagement, AdminStudentManagement
public class Admin
extends User
implements java.io.Serializable, AdminCourseManagement, AdminStudentManagement

Entity: Logic for Admin

Contains methods that allow the various implementations of an administrator such as creating and deleting a a course or student, updating the student access time, and printing details of students and indices.
